x^3-1=0
z_1 = (a+b\omega),\,z_2=(c+d\omega)\in R
 (a+b\omega)(c+d\omega)=ad\omega+bc\omega-bd\omega+ac= ac+\left( ad+bc-bd \right) \omega=g+h\omega \in R, 
 g=ac, h= ad+bc-bd \in \mathbb{Z}
